N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 268.3 - Prohibition

State Regulations

No person, corporation or other entity shall sell, offer or
expose for sale directly to consumers food products containing nitrous oxide
except in tamper-evident packaging. Notes
